ranked_sentences.sentence: The Atlanta Hawks crushed the Chicago Bulls in a thrilling match on November 10, 2024.
I can't wait to see how many three-pointers Trae Young will score against the Bulls!
I bet the fans in Chicago won't be happy after that last quarter meltdown.
The referees did a terrible job, obviously they were biased.
Nike's new jerseys for the Hawks looked pretty nice.
